extendedInfo.description: Instagram tags.This awesome app will give your Instagram photos more likes and followers in no-time and improve the visibility of your photos.Loads of tag categories with over 100 different tags in total. The app is very easy to use but yet it looks beautiful.Copy the tags easily and open Instagram on just one tap within the app.Features: Open Instagram with a single button press. Add your own custom tags. Browse popular Instagram websites with the inbuilt web browser. Browse 15+ different categories with over 100 of tags. Change the application's background and font - customize the app how you like it.In-app help and tips. Good looking and simple to use layout.
